{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifyGConnection","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxyRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO12DBusProxyRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusProxyRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyGConnection"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::g-connection"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusproxyprotocol\/onnotifygconnection(flags:handler:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxyProtocol\/onNotifyGConnection(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"onNotifyGConnection(flags:handler:)","extendedModule":"GIO","externalID":"s:3GIO17DBusProxyProtocolPAAE19onNotifyGConnection5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AG09ParamSpecN0VtctF","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyGConnection"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO12DBusProxyRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusProxyRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"type